1
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:52,620
=Endless Love=

2
00:00:52,660 --> 00:00:55,580
=Episode 12=

3
00:00:57,320 --> 00:00:57,920
Ke'er.

4
00:00:58,200 --> 00:00:59,439
What is it all about?

5
00:00:59,880 --> 00:01:01,960
How did you foresee everything?

6
00:01:02,399 --> 00:01:03,679
Ever since you went to the palace,

7
00:01:04,040 --> 00:01:05,840
I've been hiding near the music house.

8
00:01:06,400 --> 00:01:07,680
When Zhao Sisi went there

9
00:01:07,920 --> 00:01:09,319
and started asking around about you,

10
00:01:09,959 --> 00:01:11,000
I sneaked in there

11
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:12,480
to learn of their conspiracy.

12
00:01:12,959 --> 00:01:14,319
That's how I was able to report

13
00:01:14,599 --> 00:01:16,319
every detail to you,

14
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:17,840
so you could guard against it
in advance.

15
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:19,400
I don't want to see innocent people

16
00:01:19,560 --> 00:01:20,680
hurt because of me.

17
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:24,200
Earning even a sliver of Ling Xiao's trust
was no easy feat.

18
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:26,200
If my identity is exposed,

19
00:01:26,959 --> 00:01:29,000
I fear everything will be in vain.

20
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:35,280
Your Highness,

21
00:01:36,040 --> 00:01:38,799
I've been standing guard
and keeping watch outside.

22
00:01:39,799 --> 00:01:41,040
Don't worry too much.

23
00:01:42,319 --> 00:01:43,439
Ling Xiao and I went

24
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:44,959
to the dungeon
where my mother is imprisoned.

25
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:47,599
I saw her.

26
00:01:48,159 --> 00:01:49,280
How is Her Majesty?

27
00:01:49,519 --> 00:01:51,840
Mother is suffering.

28
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:54,000
Ling Xiao tortures her every day,

29
00:01:56,079 --> 00:01:57,480
but there's nothing I can do.

30
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:01,599
Your Highness.

31
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:03,840
This is not the time for grief.

32
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:07,799
I drew a map from memory

33
00:02:08,479 --> 00:02:11,080
of the path to
where my mother is imprisoned.

34
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:13,560
Win or lose,

35
00:02:14,639 --> 00:02:15,879
this is our only chance.

36
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,919
You've been through so much,
Your Highness.

37
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:21,840
I hope we can rescue Her Majesty soon

38
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,240
and return to how things used to be.

39
00:02:25,639 --> 00:02:26,680
We can never

40
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:29,039
go back to the way things were.

41
00:02:30,199 --> 00:02:31,439
Let's rescue my mother

42
00:02:33,199 --> 00:02:34,479
before talking about the future.

43
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:38,879
Your Highness,

44
00:02:39,439 --> 00:02:41,960
keep the pill safe in the pouch.

45
00:02:42,439 --> 00:02:44,759
It will prove useful
when the time comes.

46
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:26,840
Your Majesty!

47
00:03:43,639 --> 00:03:44,199
Your Majesty.

48
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:52,879
Liuli,

49
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:54,719
you are acting strange.

50
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,199
You've become so hard to read.

51
00:03:58,159 --> 00:04:00,199
Your Majesty,
you are always guarded around me.

52
00:04:01,199 --> 00:04:02,520
Whatever I say won't change anything.

53
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:07,120
I've seen you
through the window several times.

54
00:04:08,199 --> 00:04:10,039
You came to the Ruyi Palace,

55
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,360
but never entered.

56
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,319
I imagine Your Majesty

57
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:15,520
shares the same worries as I do.

58
00:04:18,279 --> 00:04:19,079
In these days,

59
00:04:19,279 --> 00:04:21,160
have I been deliberately cold
toward you,

60
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:22,959
or is it that

61
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:25,480
you can't face me either?

62
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:31,040
Are you still holding a grudge

63
00:04:31,959 --> 00:04:33,040
over the false accusation?

64
00:04:39,160 --> 00:04:40,480
(Could they be after Ke'er?)

65
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:42,680
No need to keep these matters
from Consort Li.

66
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:44,959
All city gates are locked now.

67
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:46,480
We await only your command,
Your Majesty.

68
00:04:51,839 --> 00:04:52,439
Liuli,

69
00:04:54,079 --> 00:04:55,480
I need to attend to some matters now.

70
00:04:56,959 --> 00:04:59,079
I don't care about
Zhao Sisi's false accusations.

71
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,319
And I certainly don't believe

72
00:05:00,879 --> 00:05:02,319
that with just a few words,

73
00:05:02,759 --> 00:05:04,839
she could doom me forever.

74
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:08,160
What I care about is Your Majesty.

75
00:05:08,879 --> 00:05:10,560
You once promised me

76
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:13,639
that you would trust me
with all your heart.

77
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:18,079
Perhaps I haven't tried hard enough.

78
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:20,680
I don't know how

79
00:05:21,199 --> 00:05:23,399
to lay my heart bare before you.

80
00:05:30,399 --> 00:05:31,680
I was wrong to doubt you.

81
00:05:37,079 --> 00:05:39,240
From now on, I will keep my word.

82
00:05:40,399 --> 00:05:41,279
I will never abandon you.

83
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:46,439
Your Majesty, you're hurt.

84
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:47,360
I'm fine.

85
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,360
Just some scratch.

86
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:50,639
Please take a seat.

87
00:05:50,879 --> 00:05:51,839
Let me tend to your wounds.

88
00:05:59,639 --> 00:06:01,560
Why didn't you tell me you were hurt?

89
00:06:02,839 --> 00:06:04,399
It looks quite deep.

90
00:06:05,879 --> 00:06:07,279
It pains me to see your wound.

91
00:06:08,199 --> 00:06:09,079
For men like us,

92
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:11,240
who have fought on battlefields
since childhood,

93
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:13,560
it's just a scratch.

94
00:06:14,199 --> 00:06:14,920
No worries.

95
00:06:17,519 --> 00:06:18,480
I wish that

96
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:20,240
Your Majesty will never
be wounded again.

97
00:06:22,759 --> 00:06:25,959
And I wish we could share
both joy and hardship together.

98
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,360
What are you doing?

99
00:07:07,959 --> 00:07:09,160
Mo Shuo!

100
00:07:09,519 --> 00:07:11,519
You lied to me about being
just an ordinary military physician.

101
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:12,439
No, Ke'er,

102
00:07:12,519 --> 00:07:13,279
I can explain.

103
00:07:14,439 --> 00:07:15,319
Who are you, really?

104
00:07:15,639 --> 00:07:16,839
Why were you
searching through my belongings?

105
00:07:18,199 --> 00:07:19,360
No, I wasn't.

106
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:20,920
You're still trying to deny it!

107
00:07:21,319 --> 00:07:22,240
I saw it all!

108
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:24,600
- No...
- From the very beginning,

109
00:07:25,439 --> 00:07:26,439
you've been deceiving me.

110
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:29,000
A military physician?

111
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:31,600
That was just a front
to get close to me!

112
00:07:31,839 --> 00:07:32,399
No!

113
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:33,519
Ke'er, you have to trust me.

114
00:07:34,279 --> 00:07:36,040
Read the letter, and you'll see.

115
00:07:36,319 --> 00:07:38,000
My feelings for you are genuine.

116
00:07:40,319 --> 00:07:41,040
If you still don't believe me,

117
00:07:41,519 --> 00:07:43,319
then take my life.

118
00:07:45,100 --> 00:07:47,860
(Ke'er, I pour my heart out. When will
you grant me your grace? From Mo Shuo)

119
00:07:53,519 --> 00:07:55,120
I misunderstood.

120
00:07:59,000 --> 00:07:59,759
You should go now.

121
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:01,480
I'll have a rest.

122
00:08:22,839 --> 00:08:26,120
(I pour my heart out.)

123
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:30,720
(When will you grant me your grace?)

124
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:32,639
I was overthinking.

125
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:34,679
I've wronged him.

126
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:44,159
Consort Li, you're awake.

127
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:45,759
His Majesty has invited you

128
00:08:45,919 --> 00:08:47,279
for lunch at the Ruyi Palace today.

129
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:49,720
His Majesty has arranged
for your favorite dishes to be served.

130
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:51,759
I see.

131
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:53,960
What time is it now?

132
00:08:54,399 --> 00:08:55,840
It's already noon, My Lady.

133
00:08:56,879 --> 00:08:58,039
I don't know why,

134
00:08:58,039 --> 00:09:00,000
but I've been so drowsy lately.

135
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,559
And I have no appetite at all.

136
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:04,440
I must go to His Majesty.

137
00:09:04,799 --> 00:09:06,039
I can't keep him waiting.

138
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:16,799
Your Majesty.

139
00:09:18,039 --> 00:09:18,720
Easy.

140
00:09:19,759 --> 00:09:20,919
Your wound hasn't fully healed yet.

141
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:23,440
I'm much better now.

142
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:25,320
I was just unusually tired yesterday,

143
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:26,360
so I woke up late.

144
00:09:26,919 --> 00:09:28,159
Please don't be displeased,
Your Majesty.

145
00:09:29,799 --> 00:09:30,759
It's just the two of us now,

146
00:09:31,399 --> 00:09:32,840
forget about the manners.

147
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,159
Come, have a seat.

148
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:39,519
These are your favorite pastries.

149
00:09:39,759 --> 00:09:41,440
Take one

150
00:09:41,799 --> 00:09:42,480
and try it.

151
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:49,320
How is it?

152
00:09:52,279 --> 00:09:52,759
Is it...

153
00:09:55,799 --> 00:09:56,399
Liuli,

154
00:09:57,399 --> 00:09:58,039
what's wrong?

155
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:00,279
Summon the imperial physician!

156
00:10:14,519 --> 00:10:16,120
I never knew Mo Shuo

157
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:17,840
had it in him.

158
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:29,679
Ke'er.

159
00:10:30,759 --> 00:10:31,919
Have you thought about it?

160
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:33,879
I'm not hungry right now,

161
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,879
I'll just eat whatever you make.

162
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:38,080
That's not what I'm talking about.

163
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:39,960
I mean

164
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:42,360
the letter.

165
00:10:43,679 --> 00:10:44,960
You said you once had a home,

166
00:10:45,519 --> 00:10:46,639
but it's gone now.

167
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:50,320
Please give me a chance,

168
00:10:51,679 --> 00:10:52,879
and I will give you a new one.

169
00:10:53,759 --> 00:10:54,679
I'll protect you.

170
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:05,240
I can't say yes to that now,

171
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:07,039
Mo Shuo.

172
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:08,960
Why?

173
00:11:10,799 --> 00:11:12,639
I have something
far more important to do.

174
00:11:13,799 --> 00:11:14,759
And besides,

175
00:11:16,039 --> 00:11:17,480
I've never thought about my future,

176
00:11:19,039 --> 00:11:20,519
much less love.

177
00:11:20,799 --> 00:11:21,919
What could be

178
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:23,919
more important than your future?

179
00:11:24,519 --> 00:11:25,759
I owe my life to someone.

180
00:11:27,399 --> 00:11:29,080
If she hadn't taken me in as a child,

181
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,639
I'd be dead by now.

182
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:33,320
So,

183
00:11:33,879 --> 00:11:35,279
now that she's in danger,

184
00:11:36,480 --> 00:11:38,120
I will protect her with my life.

185
00:11:45,639 --> 00:11:47,039
That's why I can't say yes now.

186
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:50,159
I'm sorry.

187
00:11:55,919 --> 00:11:58,080
A vow of gratitude
doesn't have to define your entire life.

188
00:11:58,840 --> 00:11:59,879
Do you really want to spend your life

189
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:02,399
living for someone else's plans,

190
00:12:02,639 --> 00:12:04,159
bound to them even in death?

191
00:12:07,759 --> 00:12:08,960
You can also have

192
00:12:09,159 --> 00:12:10,799
a life and happiness of your own.

193
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:24,759
Please leave, Mo Shuo.

194
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:26,679
For people like me,

195
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:29,840
fate is already written.

196
00:12:30,919 --> 00:12:32,279
It's not something I can change alone.
